Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:09.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:12.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:16.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:24.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:34.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:41.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:48.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:56.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:59.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:07.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:10.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:14.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:21.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:25.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:29.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:32.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:35.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:41.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's trying to defy the Franky Family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Give me the money back"? Then are\Nyou one of the Straw Hat's underlings?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Bro! Since he's with\NStraw Hat Luffy, I expected him to be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a really strong pirate, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit you've got guts to come\Nto get the money back all by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't let you have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to... have our ship repaired...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:03:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That money is crucial to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that money, we can finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can finally repair the Merry's scars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you jerks have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:25.14,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Rescuing Our Friend!\NRaid on the Franky House"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so worked up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you love your ship quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter what happens to your ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this money is already ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you, no matter what we\Nsteal from pirates, we won't be accused
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of committing a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dirty money that you stole\Nfrom somewhere anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:04:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let us have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, try begging the Navy for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the ones who'll be captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for Straw Hat Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that he has a useless underling\Nwho can't even watch over money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, have some fun with him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take this money\Nand go shopping at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Special Attack! Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this, long-nosed boy.\NMy name is Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:05:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to leave this town alive,\Nyou shouldn't cross me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What're you doing?! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a pathetic weapon wouldn't work on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Long-nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the 200 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it... back to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give it back to me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:06:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it... back to me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to hold out until Robin comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only become a burden to\Nthem if I march in with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be scary, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I'll protect this ship and\Nthe 100 million Berries all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you... guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:07:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right, this should be\Nthe place Nami-san was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. This is the backstreet shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go up this canal... and here!\NUsopp is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Nami-san, where can we find these\Ndemolition workers, the Franky Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? Didn't you just\Nscrew up the directions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not you! Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What'd you say?!\N--Ah, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! He just walked off\Nwithout waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:55.54,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ahhh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!\NWhere'd you come falling from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shipyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was jumping around imitating this\None shipwright to look for Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. We've got a problem, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp got abducted along with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. We're on our way to their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp got beaten up and had\Nthe money stolen from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that he felt responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and went to pick a fight with\Nthe Franky Family all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then... I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what a stubborn man he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we don't know\Nwhether he has it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they send me out this far each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish people would put themselves in my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kalifa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be worn out, Iceberg-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some tea today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Just as I'd expect from you, Kalifa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Corgy is always angry\Nwhen he leaves, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth does he come to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:10:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants something I have,\Nso he suggests all sorts of deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be something very precious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I always tell him that I don't know\Nwhat he's talking about and refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really are a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he breathing, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he's completely\Nunconscious, he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be okay. I can save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a bit... Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go blow that stupid house away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Go get more food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The alcohol today sure tastes good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've drawn graffiti on the walls of\Npeople's houses for all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! So you took my goggles back from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you a story about when I bravely\Nfought Sea Kings in the Calm Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big ones! They were...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And what's more...\NI have 8,000 men under me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That large amount of money... They stole it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't face everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:13:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you beat up every one of them, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go buy some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you buy all the food at\Nthe store, okay?! We've got money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. Just you wait and see.\NI'll beat you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:14:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you jerks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you came to get the\Nmoney back, huh, you fools?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See all the guys here? What do\Nyou think the four of you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well... you're here.\NYou've got a bounty on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you leave\Nthat head of yours with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the captain of that weak long-nosed guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't be that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's punching? At that huge steel armor\Nthat even a battleship cannon can't shatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're just fooling around,\NI'll go ahead and crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:16:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He punched a hole in that huge armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a sec, you guys! Let's have a talk first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's... Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fire cannonballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Raven...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The cannonballs are made of iron, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a cannon, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news! These guys are seriously bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get out of here!\NGet out through the back door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You started the fight. Don't act pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Party Table...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kick Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We can't use the back door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windows! Get out through the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Horn Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roseo Colonnade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait a sec, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The money, right?!\NYou want the money back, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 200 million Berries that\Nworthless guy had, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, that money is no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss, Franky, took that\Nmoney and went shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's buying something\Non the black market,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't know where he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, no matter how much\Nyou go on a rampage here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that 200 million Berries won't come ba--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Zambai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough out of you.\NIt has nothing to do with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll beat you up so bad that\Nnot even your bones will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even our bones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't get frightened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not even your bones will remain"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is what we, the Franky Family,\Ndemolition workers and bounty hunters, say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show them the Franky House's specialty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything Shot Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come! Attack them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't flinch! Keep firing\Nuntil we run out of cannonballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only four of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're those noises? Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the northeast! They're coming\Nfrom the direction of the Franky House!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Them again? What's the fuss about this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yea... Ugh! Shh! He'll hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy, they're getting too carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really don't show any\Nrestraint when they party, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay once in a while, right?\NIt's a wonderful day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go follow Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat. Looks like they really\Ndon't know where the money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we strangle this Franky guy,\Nif he already spent the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do now? Even if we wait for\Nhim here, he won't be back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I finished giving him first aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to take him on a stretcher,\Nso help me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Staying here talking won't get us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the ship for now.\NWe left Nami-san alone there, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have the thing with\NRobin-chan to deal with...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the issues with the ship, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say goodbye... to the Going Merry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:08.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, you're taking the joke too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.59,0:23:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll say goodbye to the Merry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull! Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship can't be fixed anymore!\NShe'll sink soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--No matter what you say,\NI'm never gonna give up on Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Big Fight under the Moon!\NThe Pirate Flag Flutters with Sorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
